  "text": "The rules of the holographic correspondence then tell us that the bulk theory is a pure 5D Yang-Mills with gauge group SU(3) L × SU(3) R , with boundary conditions on the UV boundary z = L 0 such that the zero modes of the SU(3) L × SU(3) R gauge fields are eliminated, and no 4D gauge symmetry survives, only a 4D global SU(3) L × SU(3) R subgroup. The Lagrangian is given by [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ",
